<h2 id="python获取激光雷达数据">python获取激光雷达数据</h2>
<blockquote>
<p>Written with <a href="https://stackedit.cn/">StackEdit中文版</a>.<br>
<img alt="输入图片说明" src="data:image/png;base64,"></p>
</blockquote>
<p>1.下载启智机器人的包</p>
<pre><code>cd ~/catkin_ws/src/
git clone https://github.com/6-robot/wpr_simulation.git
</code></pre>
<p>2.构建lidar_pkg软件包</p>
<pre><code>cd ~/catkin_ws/src
catkin_create_pkg lidar_pkg roscpp rospy sensor_msgs
</code></pre>
<p>3.创建lidar_node.py</p>
<pre><code>#!/usr/bin/env python3

# coding=utf-8

  

import rospy

from sensor_msgs.msg import LaserScan

  

# 激光雷达回调函数

def lidar_callback(msg):

number = len(msg.ranges)

rospy.loginfo("雷达测距数量 = %d",number)

middle = number//2

rospy.logwarn("正前方测距数值 = %f 米",msg.ranges[middle])

  

# 主函数

if __name__ == "__main__":

rospy.init_node("lidar_data")

# 订阅激光雷达的数据话题

lidar_sub = rospy.Subscriber("scan",LaserScan,lidar_callback,queue_size=10)

rospy.spin()
</code></pre>
<ol start="4">
<li>编译</li>
</ol>
<pre><code>catkin_make
</code></pre>
<ol start="5">
<li>测试<br>
开启模拟场景</li>
</ol>
<pre><code>roslaunch wpr_simulation wpr1_simple.launch
</code></pre>
<p>在打开一个terminal，获取雷达数据</p>
<pre><code>cd ~/catkin_ws
source devel/setup.bash
rosrun lidar_pkg lidar_node.py
</code></pre>
